{"tid":1328131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[奔雷手文泰來] TVB綠葉鄭家生單拖挑機　喝停示威者：搞到香港亂晒","createTime":"2019-07-17T23:28:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T02:05:19.000Z","uid":224066,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"fb783d43d60cb846485a49367f5e67a528307b6a","tid":1328131,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T23:28:04.000Z","msg":"因為一條逃犯條例，最近香港發生多次遊行示威，示威活動延至沙田，日前於新城市廣場發生騷亂事件，警方和市民都有多人受傷。這兩日，都有不少市民前往新城市廣場要求商場的物業管理員交代當日事件，並且圍着商場保安。TVB金牌綠葉鄭家生在今日傍晚時間經過新城市廣場，<span style=\"color: red;\">目擊保安被圍經過，上前喝止市民，不過卻被市民者反過來罵他是「茄哩啡」。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3047509/org/7e56bbdd450e2ddb4be85be505f3d8bb.jpg/mhTK_BepptcAj3MCUL-iJDsofkcR00kOi3FyhItxcoQ?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3047509%2Forg%2F7e56bbdd450e2ddb4be85be505f3d8bb.jpg%2FmhTK_BepptcAj3MCUL-iJDsofkcR00kOi3FyhItxcoQ%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=f37e643a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3047513/org/5cf743d32aa4283754a94f5a4086c2be.jpg/iYj6NlEZH1F38p5RuTuv2LEQaIMhmEpuHPtquhz7aro\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3047513%2Forg%2F5cf743d32aa4283754a94f5a4086c2be.jpg%2FiYj6NlEZH1F38p5RuTuv2LEQaIMhmEpuHPtquhz7aro&h=1e669056&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3047419/org/b145dd664d4f8a88e72075037a6ea492.jpg/BMeI7gCd8vxlzZOp1Cz-N-i_8PXTRB04QtnC7GTZwuw?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3047419%2Forg%2Fb145dd664d4f8a88e72075037a6ea492.jpg%2FBMeI7gCd8vxlzZOp1Cz-N-i_8PXTRB04QtnC7GTZwuw%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=cd6b5df9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鄭家生表示現在香港太亂，再這樣下去香港會散，他說：「而家啲人都好離譜，搞到香港亂晒，係咪要令到解放軍落嚟，美國佬咪開心囉。我去到班人面前，叫佢哋唔好圍，佢哋就係咪鬧我，話我茄哩啡，我咪話：『你打我囉！』佢哋緊係唔敢喇。其實咁樣落去大家都死，我覺得呢班人應該靜一靜，<span style=\"color: red;\">呢班人都係搞事，和平示威啲人都散晒喇。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3047428/org/d0e9964e9892d3c1f0de0bac31028876.jpg/XqWvwCGz6A2RmxP8ea6RxgdC3np4PbGgHd7Pix3ez4s?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3047428%2Forg%2Fd0e9964e9892d3c1f0de0bac31028876.jpg%2FXqWvwCGz6A2RmxP8ea6RxgdC3np4PbGgHd7Pix3ez4s%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=d456d119&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2778687/org/45f78dd11b47bde95f583be9fdae1e43.jpg/Qf45U26lxD2Z0ERcBO7xuc65IUDel48yEHbatxB22rc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2778687%2Forg%2F45f78dd11b47bde95f583be9fdae1e43.jpg%2FQf45U26lxD2Z0ERcBO7xuc65IUDel48yEHbatxB22rc&h=be523661&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cf8f3981f4acb45c291bea6472c26916a84cd228","tid":1328131,"uid":224066,"like":4,"dislike":10,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T23:29:10.000Z","msg":"《香港01》致電鄭家生了解事件，他指自己做完gym後經過新城市廣場，發現一班人圍着商場保安，便上前喝前他們：「佢哋（市民）圍住啲保安要人交代，交代啲乜啫，電視都影晒喇，嗰日我喺電視了解事件（7月14日），其實乜都影晒喇，啲人都唔通氣，恃住人多就圍人、靠惡，唔講道理。」鄭家生更表示，他見到一名年青人，在現場不停叫店舖落閘，他指：「當自己指揮官啊？人哋唔使做生意咩！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/353232/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-tvb%E7%B6%A0%E8%91%89%E9%84%AD%E5%AE%B6%E7%94%9F%E5%96%AE%E6%8B%96%E6%8C%91%E6%A9%9F-%E5%96%9D%E5%81%9C%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85-%E6%90%9E%E5%88%B0%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%82%E6%99%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F353232%2F%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-tvb%25E7%25B6%25A0%25E8%2591%2589%25E9%2584%25AD%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2596%25AE%25E6%258B%2596%25E6%258C%2591%25E6%25A9%259F-%25E5%2596%259D%25E5%2581%259C%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585-%25E6%2590%259E%25E5%2588%25B0%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%2582%25E6%2599%2592&d=bTkwEGnHH2OXdpYsGZaaktqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=9db44